## Payload + Next.js (this repo)

- **CMS data:** `getPayload` / Local API from Server Components and Route Handlers — **`depth`**, **`select`**, cache keys → **`payload-basics.mdc`**, **`payload-performance.mdc`**, `utilities/getDocument.ts`.
- **Next-only:** middleware-level concerns, **`draftMode`**, **`cookies`** / **`headers`**, App Router caching **`unstable_cache`** / **`revalidateTag`**, **`next.config.js`**, OpenNext — topic rules **`next-caching-revalidation.mdc`**, **`next-config-adapters-turbopack.mdc`**, **`next-deployment.mdc`** + **`payload-deployment.mdc`** for CI/migrate/wrangler.

## Repo map (Next layer)

| Path / artifact | Role |
|-----------------|------|
| **`src/app`** | App Router tree |
| **`next.config.js`** | `withPayload`, images, webpack + Turbopack aliases |
| **`open-next.config.ts`** | OpenNext Cloudflare overrides (cache, queue, tag cache) |
| **Build scripts** | `scripts/build.mjs`, `deploymentTarget`, `nextBuildPipeline` — **`payload-deployment.mdc`** |

## Reading discipline

Follow **`agent-read-rules.mdc`**. For Next-only tasks, open **`next-features-overview.mdc`** and the listed **`next-*.mdc`** files — do not read every Next topic up front.

**Regenerating other `next-*.mdc` (not this file):** `pnpm generate:cursor-rules:next` — sources `scripts/definitions/next-bodies/*.md`, `scripts/definitions/next-cursor-rules.manifest.json`, and the hub table in `scripts/generate-next-cursor-rules.mjs`.

